What is Sorting?

Definition: Sorting refers to arranging data in particular format: either
ascending or descending.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Practical uses of Sorting:

Microsoft excel - Has an inbuilt functionality to sort data.
Online Stores - one stores generally have option of sorting search result  by
Price, Review, Ratings, etc.


